ogical but bad. } 20... a4 $1 { A very instructive pawn sacrifice: we are solid enough on the kingside and can launch an immediate attack. } 21. Nxh5 gxh5 22. Bxh5 b3 $17 { [%cal Ba6d3,Be7a3]This is very similar to the main line with 21.Bxh5 (See the corresponding variation from the PGN). } * 

