... Rxb8 17. h4 h6 $1 18. Ne2 hxg5 19. hxg5 g6 $1 { No need to take on g5 just yet. } 20. f4 Kg7 21. Kb1 Rbd8 $1 22. Bg2 e5 $1 { Disrupting White's central structure. } 23. fxe5 Bxg5 { The endgame is equal; White's extra pawn is not really significant. } * 

