6, because then c3 falls and the knight can go to d5. } 19. Rhe1 ( 19. Bxb6 { can be met with } 19... Nxc3 $146 { . } ) 19... bxa5 20. Rxe4 Bc6 21. Re2 Bd5 $10 { The position is half-blocked and with opposite color bishops on the board Black did not have any problems in Shirov - Movsesian, Loo 2014. } * 

