and the endgame is just too unpleasant. } ) 14. Nb3 $1 { A very precise move, vacating the d4-square for White's bishop. Otherwise, Black equalizes very comfortably. } 14... Nc4 15. Bc5 { This avoids ...O-O, but does not put pressure on the a1-h8 diagonal. } 15... Ne4 $1 16. O-O-O Be6 { [%cal Gf7f5,Ge8c8]...O-O is not available, but we can castle long. Our position is fine. } * 

