es White has created on the kingside. } 15. Bd4 Bxd4 16. Rxd4 Ng3 $1 17. Rg1 Bb7 { ½-½ Stankovic, M - Perunovic, M Novi, 2023. This precise defense has already been demonstrated in practice by none other than Taimanov expert Milos Perunovic. } * 

