ght with ...g6. } 15... g6 16. Be4 Qc7 17. Bxb7 Qxb7 18. Nf2 { White improves their bad knight on d1 to e4. } 18... f6 $1 { We do the same! We want to bring the knight on h5 back into the game. } 19. exf6 Nxf6 $13 { [%cal Ge8g8,Ga8c8]Position is complex, and although we have a slightly weaker pawn structure, our position is completely playable. } * 

