means the plan initiated with ...Ba3 has been a success, as White can no longer castle long so easily. } 11... d6 12. Ne2 { Otherwise, White could not untangle themself. } 12... Bb4+ $1 13. c3 Bc5 { I think it makes sense including ...Bb4+ before playing ...Bc5: the pawn should give us a hook on b4 in case White goes for long-castling. } 14. Nd4 Qc7 $13 { Black has a perfectly fine Sicilian position, and White's queen and pawn on c3 look awkward and out of place for this type of structure. } * 

