ous for us, but as we have seen many times already, things work tactically for Black! I do not think this is coincidence or luck: all of our pieces are harmoniously deployed and we have a strong center. } 18... Qc8 19. Kh1 Nf5 20. Be5 Bxe5 21. fxe5 Qb8 $13 { [%cal Gb8e5,Ge5g7]Black wins a pawn and the queen can come to the defend the kingside if needed. We should avoid the temptation to win the exchange. } ( 21... Ne3 $2 $146 22. Qd2 Nxf1 $146 23. Qg5+ Kh8 24. Nd6 $146 ) * 

