 for ...Re8-d8 set-up, but ...Rd8-Rc8 looks more harmonious. } ) 16. Kh1 Rac8 17. Qe3 $6 { White should probably keep pressure on the d6-pawn to avoid our knight maneuvers. } 17... Nd7 $1 18. Bg4 Re8 19. Qg3 Ne5 $133 { [%cal Ge5g6]} * 

