I want to show you a nice resource after some logical moves, that of course you do not need to memorize, but it can give an idea of how the play can go. } 16. Bf3 Rc8 17. Kg2 Nf6 18. e5 dxe5 19. fxe5 { Now Nh7 would be passive, but we have an idea in store. } 19... h4 $41 { And White faces already big problems, because taking the knight is of course not possible. } * 

