 suddenly very safe, and we have counterplay on both sides of the board. The engine already evaluates the position close to 0.00, even though we are a pawn down! You don't have to memorize what follows, but it can give you an idea of how the game might proceed. } 23. Qxe5 fxe5 { [%cal Ge6a2]} 24. a3 b5 $1 25. c3 b4 26. axb4 axb4 27. cxb4 Rhb8 $10 { [%cal Gb8b4,Ga8a2]Black is too active for White to make anything of their extra pawn. } * 

