t the repertoire on several occasions. Opening up the b7-bishop is worth more than a pawn. } 19. Bxd4 O-O-O $13 { [%cal Gh8h6,Gh6g6,Gd8h8][%csl Rd4]The position is very complex, but it looks like more fun for Black with the powerful bishops! } * 

