1. e4 c5 2. a3 { Not very impressive. White wants to play b4, so we are going to play with ...g6 to bother him. } 2... g6 3. h4 { Very modern-looking, but not very impressive. } 3... Nf6 4. e5 Nh5 { Intending to go ...Nc6, ...Qc7, & ...d6 with pressure on e5. } 5. g4 { This primitive move does not bother us too much. } 5... Ng7 6. h5 gxh5 7. gxh5 Nc6 $17 { [%cal Gd7d6,Gg7f5,Gd8c7,Gf8g7]Only moving pawns in the first seven moves has not brought any happiness to White! } * 

